column2: SELECT TOP # Artist.Name as artist, SUM(Track.UnitPrice) as price FROM chinook.Track INNER JOIN chinook.Album on chinook.Album.AlbumId=chinook.Track.AlbumId INNER JOIN chinook.Artist on chinook.Artist.ArtistId=chinook.Track.ArtistId GROUP BY Artist.Name, Track.UnitPrice ORDER BY SUM(Track.UnitPrice) DESC
